gui

Class MazeColor

  • java.lang.Object
    • gui.MazeColor

  • public class MazeColor
extends java.lang.Object
    MazeColor helps MazePanel to convert between its own color representation and Color. For forthcoming projects, this can be easily refactored to work with Android color representations.
    Author:
    Elijah Mas
